WEBVTT

00:41.125 --> 00:43.461
<i>I hope someone finds this.</i>

00:43.794 --> 00:48.339
<i>No one said or did anything to stop them.</i>

00:48.340 --> 00:50.760
<i>It’s too late for me.</i>

00:51.093 --> 00:52.470
<i>I was alone.</i>

00:53.512 --> 00:55.306
<i>It may not be too late for you.</i>

03:40.638 --> 03:42.013
Come on!

03:48.646 --> 03:51.482
<i>America's changed,
you understand that?</i>

03:52.691 --> 03:55.735
<i>I think to create the perfect
union of democracy</i>

03:55.736 --> 03:58.072
<i>has been a struggle...</i>

04:32.481 --> 04:34.107
<i>Dear passengers,</i>

04:34.108 --> 04:36.859
<i>people who behave disorderly
in public areas</i>

04:36.860 --> 04:39.446
<i>will be punished according
to regulations,</i>

04:39.655 --> 04:41.907
<i>and their behaviour will be recorded.</i>

04:42.074 --> 04:45.368
<i>To avoid any negative record
of personal credit,</i>

04:45.369 --> 04:47.704
<i>please follow the relevant regulations.</i>

05:27.494 --> 05:30.205
So, whatever else happens now,
it’s all in a day’s work.

07:02.172 --> 07:04.675
<i>I can still remember my grandma.</i>

07:10.430 --> 07:12.849
<i>I used to help her out.</i>

07:12.850 --> 07:14.559
<i>My grandma used to say her memories</i>

07:14.560 --> 07:18.105
<i>were slipping through
her fingers like sand.</i>

07:18.814 --> 07:20.440
<i>She said, we didn’t know it,</i>

07:21.483 --> 07:23.986
<i>but that was happening to all of us too.</i>

07:25.362 --> 07:29.867
<i>She said soon,
there’d be no past, no history.</i>

07:31.160 --> 07:35.247
<i>She said it was the truth,
and she didn’t care who heard.</i>

07:36.748 --> 07:39.668
<i>Then one day, they came for her,</i>

07:40.878 --> 07:43.505
<i>and she was gone.</i>

07:46.758 --> 07:48.927
<i>That stabbed to the heart of me,</i>

07:49.761 --> 07:51.805
<i>it silenced me.</i>

07:52.181 --> 07:54.099
<i>I never spoke again.</i>

07:56.643 --> 07:58.270
<i>I ran.</i>

08:01.481 --> 08:03.025
<i>I’m still running.</i>

08:17.789 --> 08:20.374
<i>My life’s turned into
one of those sci-fi comics</i>

08:20.375 --> 08:21.793
<i>I used to read.</i>

08:23.503 --> 08:25.088
<i>I live off-grid.</i>

08:27.883 --> 08:31.220
<i>My place is in Shoes,
on the lower ground.</i>

08:38.018 --> 08:39.811
<i>There are others here.</i>

08:42.272 --> 08:43.774
<i>Survivors.</i>

08:45.943 --> 08:47.486
<i>Renegades.</i>

08:58.205 --> 09:00.623
Know what I'm saying?
Anyone know why I’m saying this?

09:00.624 --> 09:02.792
<i>There’s a tunnel up to Fragrances,</i>

09:02.793 --> 09:04.752
<i>where the old entrance was.</i>

09:08.757 --> 09:11.426
<i>It’s one of the six ways
up to the surface.</i>

10:18.785 --> 10:20.162
Hey, Ghost.

10:21.163 --> 10:22.331
Going up?

10:23.582 --> 10:24.832
Stay safe.

10:24.833 --> 10:27.209
<i>I met this guy, Jack,</i>

10:27.210 --> 10:30.129
<i>dumpster-diving one night.</i>

10:30.130 --> 10:31.505
<i>It was me who got him in here.</i>

10:31.506 --> 10:34.509
Hey, I’ve found an old picture
you might like.

10:36.178 --> 10:38.304
<i>He’s got these goofy,</i>
p <i>uppy dog eyes.</i>

10:38.305 --> 10:39.972
I’ll show it to you later.

10:39.973 --> 10:41.558
<i>He’s an AI.</i>

10:42.267 --> 10:43.477
Stay safe.

10:44.728 --> 10:47.813
<i>He listens and watches everything.</i>

10:51.068 --> 10:53.070
<i>You can’t trust anyone anymore.</i>

11:01.078 --> 11:04.622
<i>When you glean up
on the surface, after curfew,</i>

11:04.623 --> 11:06.083
<i>you have to be quick.</i>

11:08.502 --> 11:10.461
<i>You avoid the dogs,</i>

11:10.462 --> 11:12.881
<i>you dodge the street militia.</i>

11:44.121 --> 11:47.164
<i>Move north,
destruction area north.</i>

11:47.165 --> 11:49.625
<i>This is now a civil disturbance.</i>

11:49.626 --> 11:52.378
<i>Failure to do so could result
in arrest and the use of force,</i>

11:52.379 --> 11:54.131
<i>including riot patrol agents and...</i>

11:56.007 --> 11:58.260
<i>People thought the world would end.</i>

12:01.930 --> 12:03.681
<i>But the world goes on.</i>

12:14.443 --> 12:16.403
<i>It's us who will end.</i>

12:20.991 --> 12:23.577
<i>...must leave
the area immediately.</i>

12:23.869 --> 12:27.371
<i>Failure to comply with this
order may subject you to arrest</i>

12:27.372 --> 12:30.458
<i>and may subject you to the use
of riot patrol agents</i>

12:30.459 --> 12:31.710
<i>or impact weapons.</i>

12:34.254 --> 12:36.381
<i>This is the police department.</i>

12:36.673 --> 12:40.010
<i>You are violating state imposed curfew.</i>

12:41.136 --> 12:44.555
<i>Go home or you will be arrested.</i>

12:57.527 --> 12:59.613
<i>Gleaning is how we get by.</i>

13:00.864 --> 13:05.118
<i>We pick over the leftovers,
the broken, the rejected...</i>

13:05.660 --> 13:07.537
<i>anything we can use.</i>

13:10.957 --> 13:14.127
Thanks, Ghost. I love it!

13:15.378 --> 13:17.255
<i>Those puppy dog eyes.</i>

13:17.672 --> 13:19.549
I love this hat.

13:45.825 --> 13:48.994
<i>I have no mercy or compassion in me</i>

13:48.995 --> 13:51.580
<i>for a society that will crush people,</i>

13:51.581 --> 13:54.792
<i>and then penalise them for not
being able to stand up</i>

13:54.793 --> 13:56.711
<i>under the weight.</i>

14:04.928 --> 14:06.054
<i>How did we get here?</i>

14:07.180 --> 14:08.639
<i>How did we let this happen?</i>

14:09.766 --> 14:11.684
In the late 1980s, early 1990s,

14:11.685 --> 14:14.729
you were in a moment of
democratic triumph.

14:15.981 --> 14:18.191
We’re now in a democratic recession,

14:19.526 --> 14:21.318
and it’s endemic in Eastern Europe,

14:21.319 --> 14:22.319
in Western Europe,

14:22.320 --> 14:24.655
in the United States, India,

14:24.656 --> 14:26.324
the Philippines.

14:26.908 --> 14:29.034
This is a new age of impunity.

14:29.035 --> 14:31.787
Some countries are actually
just going back to the age

14:31.788 --> 14:33.290
of elite power.

14:33.498 --> 14:36.333
The financial system is rocked
to its foundation,

14:36.334 --> 14:38.377
as top Wall Street institutions...

14:38.378 --> 14:41.171
If you have an economic crisis,

14:41.172 --> 14:44.049
and/or a refugee crisis,

14:44.050 --> 14:45.801
these demagogues rise.

14:45.802 --> 14:47.636
They’re promising to protect
you from a threat

14:47.637 --> 14:49.306
that doesn’t exist.

14:54.311 --> 14:56.937
You have an incredibly dishonest
right-wing media,

14:56.938 --> 14:58.355
who pushes disinformation.

15:01.151 --> 15:03.360
Hate and fear are being sown

15:03.361 --> 15:05.988
online across the world,

15:05.989 --> 15:12.037
spreading lies paid for with
illegal cash. It’s subversion.

15:16.166 --> 15:18.292
What Putin saw, is, he's like,

15:18.293 --> 15:21.046
“Holy shit, I can hack this system,

15:21.463 --> 15:24.799
and then control global
capitalism, and politics.”

15:29.554 --> 15:31.347
There are transnational oligarchs

15:31.348 --> 15:33.766
funding dark money think-tanks

15:33.767 --> 15:35.309
and fake institutions.

15:35.310 --> 15:36.935
Americans for prosperity.

15:36.936 --> 15:39.730
Renowned Washington
think-tank, the Cato Institute.

15:39.731 --> 15:41.983
The Institute of Economic Affairs.

15:42.359 --> 15:45.569
They’re lobby shops, set up
to influence politics

15:45.570 --> 15:49.866
on behalf of ideological
billionaires and big business.

15:50.116 --> 15:52.993
BP is a corporate donor to the lEA.

15:52.994 --> 15:55.371
They come to tons of our events.

15:55.372 --> 15:56.997
BP might say, you know,

15:56.998 --> 15:59.583
"We at BP are really struggling
with these regulations.

15:59.584 --> 16:02.170
Can you tell me why you're not going
to change this, Minister?"

16:02.379 --> 16:04.381
It’s disrupting democracy.

16:06.299 --> 16:09.468
Social media has enabled
the rise of these populist

16:09.469 --> 16:11.596
authoritarian-style leaders.

16:12.389 --> 16:16.308
We will root out the communists, Marxists,

16:16.309 --> 16:18.602
fascists and the radical left thugs

16:18.603 --> 16:22.774
that live like vermin within
the confines of our country.

16:24.234 --> 16:28.029
We will make America great again.

16:28.571 --> 16:30.949
Jews will not replace us!

16:31.700 --> 16:36.412
So, you would say that white
supremacist tied publications

16:36.413 --> 16:39.416
meet a rigorous standard
for fact-checking?

16:41.668 --> 16:44.378
Facebook’s site has
been used to incite violence

16:44.379 --> 16:47.090
against Rohingya refugees in Myanmar.

16:47.298 --> 16:51.511
Mr Modi has driven Muslims of
this country to the wall.

16:52.178 --> 16:54.096
I have a particular responsibility,

16:54.097 --> 16:57.516
it is to end the free movement
of people once and for all.

16:58.685 --> 17:00.185
Europe is in the heat
of a battle

17:00.186 --> 17:02.146
about the future of democracy,

17:02.147 --> 17:04.649
and Hungary is now the front line.

17:05.358 --> 17:08.235
It’s not just Putin and Orbán,

17:08.236 --> 17:10.447
there’s an alliance of dictatorships.

17:10.572 --> 17:12.740
There’s no subtlety

17:12.741 --> 17:16.744
in Netanyahu’s ambition to claim
all of the Palestinian state.

17:16.745 --> 17:18.912
There’s a global effort by people in power

17:18.913 --> 17:20.582
to stay in power.

17:21.166 --> 17:25.669
They care more about maintaining
power for their clique,

17:25.670 --> 17:28.840
than a broader sense of common good.

17:40.143 --> 17:43.354
Hitler massacred three million Jews.

17:45.774 --> 17:47.317
There's three million drug addicts,

17:50.195 --> 17:51.905
I'd be happy to slaughter them.

17:53.156 --> 17:55.908
The volume of killing
here is quite extraordinary.

17:55.909 --> 17:59.661
In the 80 or so days
that Duterte has been in power,

17:59.662 --> 18:03.540
there’s now been an average of
somewhere between 35 and 40

18:03.541 --> 18:07.669
police killings of drug-pushers
and drug users every day.

18:07.670 --> 18:10.757
So no qualms about killing killers?

18:10.965 --> 18:14.761
Yes, of course. I must admit, I have killed.

18:15.929 --> 18:18.973
I’m a journalist. This is my
37th year as a journalist.

18:19.849 --> 18:22.643
What’s the role of journalism?
Journalism, the mission:

18:22.644 --> 18:25.437
holding power to account,
public and private.

18:25.438 --> 18:29.066
As President, you now also
defend the constitution.

18:29.067 --> 18:30.526
- Yes.
- You break the law,

18:30.527 --> 18:31.777
you threaten to break the law.

18:31.778 --> 18:33.821
You said you had killed a year ago, right?

18:33.822 --> 18:34.905
You told me that,

18:34.906 --> 18:37.616
and yet you now have the task of

18:37.617 --> 18:39.034
keeping the rule of law

18:39.035 --> 18:41.037
and you said you would do
that also. How do you...?

18:41.287 --> 18:42.204
Because the rule of law

18:42.205 --> 18:43.789
there must be fear.

18:43.790 --> 18:47.668
When Duterte took office,
our institutions crumbled.

18:47.669 --> 18:50.754
He became the most powerful
person within six months.

18:50.755 --> 18:55.050
Just because you're a journalist you think
you are except from assassination.

18:55.051 --> 18:56.218
It's all wrong.

18:56.219 --> 18:58.178
We continue doing our reporting.

19:10.233 --> 19:12.192
How do you feel killing Muslims?

19:12.193 --> 19:13.235
I enjoy it.

19:13.236 --> 19:15.363
We killed them, came home and slept.

19:20.660 --> 19:22.244
<i>On the worst day of the violence,</i>

19:22.245 --> 19:24.538
<i>when murder and looting were taking place</i>

19:24.539 --> 19:28.375
<i>all across the city, we saw
policemen just standing by,</i>

19:28.376 --> 19:29.751
<i>watching what was happening</i>

19:29.752 --> 19:32.130
<i>but doing nothing to try to stop it.</i>

19:34.883 --> 19:37.092
When you look back over the last months,

19:37.093 --> 19:38.552
you’ve been the leader of this state

19:38.553 --> 19:40.220
through a very difficult period,

19:40.221 --> 19:41.388
do you think there’s anything that

19:41.389 --> 19:42.891
you should have done differently?

19:43.474 --> 19:48.855
Yes, one area where I was very, very weak,

19:48.855 --> 19:51.274
and that was how to handle the media.

19:51.858 --> 19:53.108
He doesn’t like criticism,

19:53.109 --> 19:54.067
he’s self-obsessed,

19:54.068 --> 19:55.402
he’s a megalomaniac,

19:55.403 --> 19:57.780
and I say that all the time.

19:58.698 --> 20:00.283
My name is Rana Ayyub.

20:00.617 --> 20:03.493
I’m a global opinions writer
with the Washington Post,

20:03.494 --> 20:04.912
I’m an investigative journalist.

20:04.913 --> 20:07.873
I write stuff which
the government does not like.

20:07.874 --> 20:10.083
Mr Modi is going from strength
to strength.

20:10.084 --> 20:12.920
He’s become a leader of anti-Muslim

20:12.921 --> 20:15.088
bigots across the country.

20:15.089 --> 20:16.506
I spoke about the fact that

20:16.507 --> 20:18.967
here is a man who’s an authoritarian,

20:18.968 --> 20:23.472
whose only politics is his
prejudice of Muslims,

20:23.473 --> 20:26.058
whose only politics is
persecution of Muslims,

20:26.059 --> 20:28.101
and if this man comes to power,

20:28.102 --> 20:29.645
he is going to repeat that,

20:29.646 --> 20:31.855
and that’s exactly what has transpired

20:31.856 --> 20:34.442
since Modi came to power in 2014.

20:44.410 --> 20:47.746
I believe that I’m standing up
for just bearing witness.

20:47.747 --> 20:49.456
I don’t even want to do anything.

20:49.457 --> 20:50.874
I don’t want to be anybody’s hero.

20:50.875 --> 20:52.793
I don’t want to be put on a pedestal.

20:52.794 --> 20:55.128
I just wanted to speak my truth.

21:06.599 --> 21:09.686
Nigel, Nigel, this way!

21:10.687 --> 21:11.478
Nigel!

21:11.479 --> 21:12.521
They know this referendum

21:12.522 --> 21:13.939
is too close to call,

21:13.940 --> 21:16.066
and are stepping up the intensity

21:16.067 --> 21:18.735
with just a week to go till polling day.

21:18.736 --> 21:21.405
When ISIS say they will use
the migrant crisis

21:21.406 --> 21:24.116
to flood the continent
with their Jihadi terrorists,

21:24.117 --> 21:24.992
they probably mean it.

21:24.993 --> 21:29.663
It's no good fighting
an election campaign on the facts

21:29.664 --> 21:32.416
Now, this is a once-in- a-lifetime chance

21:32.417 --> 21:35.962
for us to take back control
of our immigration system.

21:36.546 --> 21:38.547
because actually it's all about emotion.

21:38.548 --> 21:40.507
The majority of people in this country

21:40.508 --> 21:41.675
are suffering as a result of

21:41.676 --> 21:42.927
our membership of the European Union.

21:42.927 --> 21:45.804
These are things
that don't necessarily need to be true.

21:45.805 --> 21:47.390
As long as they're believed.

21:47.515 --> 21:50.517
If people feel that voting
doesn’t change anything,

21:50.518 --> 21:52.310
then violence is the next step.

22:00.153 --> 22:02.779
What I and other journalists
have uncovered

22:02.780 --> 22:05.908
is that multiple crimes took
place during the referendum.

22:06.200 --> 22:08.368
It was the biggest electoral fraud

22:08.369 --> 22:11.371
in Britain for 100 years.

22:11.372 --> 22:12.664
I’m a journalist.

22:12.665 --> 22:14.666
I kind of came into
investigative journalism

22:14.667 --> 22:16.710
accidentally, when I was a feature writer.

22:16.711 --> 22:19.254
This is what they were posting
on Facebook,

22:19.255 --> 22:21.715
paid for with illegal cash.

22:21.716 --> 22:23.592
How do you hold power to account?

22:23.593 --> 22:26.011
That’s all I’m trying to
figure out is like

22:26.012 --> 22:28.388
what are the different
mechanisms for holding

22:28.389 --> 22:29.681
power to account?

22:29.682 --> 22:31.850
Because the old ways don’t work any more.

22:31.851 --> 22:34.478
We have no idea who saw what ads,

22:34.479 --> 22:35.937
or even who placed the ads,

22:35.938 --> 22:37.731
or how much money was spent,

22:37.732 --> 22:40.401
or even what nationality they were.

22:40.610 --> 22:42.861
When I stumbled into this story,

22:42.862 --> 22:45.906
it was really like the scales
falling away from my eyes,

22:45.907 --> 22:48.658
and when I understood so much is actually

22:48.659 --> 22:51.244
controlled beyond the naked eye.

22:51.245 --> 22:52.954
If you’re interested, what I’d like to do

22:52.955 --> 22:56.958
is set up something,
and I’ll fund it somehow,

22:56.959 --> 22:59.252
that I think... and I think
you’re the perfect guy,

22:59.253 --> 23:00.545
we help knit together

23:00.546 --> 23:02.089
this populist nationalist movement

23:02.090 --> 23:03.131
throughout the world,

23:03.132 --> 23:04.549
'cause guys in Egypt are coming to me,

23:04.550 --> 23:06.218
the Modi's guys in India,

23:06.219 --> 23:11.556
Duterte, you know, and we get
Orbán, and we are somehow,

23:11.557 --> 23:13.643
some sort of convening authority.

23:14.018 --> 23:15.811
It’s a global revolt.

23:27.115 --> 23:29.866
The game-changer was the weaponisation

23:29.867 --> 23:31.077
of social media.

23:32.578 --> 23:36.124
I got 90 hate messages per hour.

23:36.791 --> 23:40.335
That’s when I began to realise,
this is really different.

23:40.336 --> 23:45.006
These tech companies enabled a real shift,

23:45.007 --> 23:51.763
because exponential lies
literally came at us so fast

23:51.764 --> 23:54.432
that our human capacity to absorb

23:54.433 --> 23:56.601
and fight back was gone.

23:58.479 --> 24:01.398
8.5 million tweets were directed
against me,

24:01.399 --> 24:05.902
in which the language is so
similar, Jihadi, burqa-clad,

24:05.903 --> 24:09.740
ISIS sex slave, you
know, terrorist sympathiser.

24:10.241 --> 24:12.952
I personally
got really targeted.

24:13.202 --> 24:17.206
There was this systemic
harassment going on online.

24:17.665 --> 24:19.959
It became overwhelming.

24:20.334 --> 24:22.294
The weaponisation of social media

24:22.295 --> 24:25.006
was quickly followed by
the weaponisation of the law.

24:25.173 --> 24:29.177
You reporters,
you will be allowed to criticise us

24:29.427 --> 24:32.512
but you will go to jail for your crime.

24:32.513 --> 24:34.222
A prominent critic of
Philippine President,

24:34.223 --> 24:36.099
Rodrigo Duterte, has been arrested.

24:36.100 --> 24:38.727
Maria Ressa is CEO and Executive Editor

24:38.728 --> 24:40.312
for the online news site, Rappler.

24:40.313 --> 24:42.772
Journalist Rana Ayyub,
who’s been a fierce critic

24:42.773 --> 24:44.983
of the government
led by Prime Minister Modi,

24:44.984 --> 24:46.985
has been named in a charge sheet filed

24:46.986 --> 24:50.114
by the Enforcement Directorate
over alleged money-laundering.

24:50.448 --> 24:51.907
Carol Cadwalladr, as a result

24:51.908 --> 24:54.201
of your reporting on Brexit,

24:54.202 --> 24:58.206
you have been sued by a British
businessman.

24:58.873 --> 25:01.583
This boys’ club
reads each other's manuals,

25:01.584 --> 25:02.918
okay, what have we done?

25:02.919 --> 25:06.129
Minorities silenced, media silenced,

25:06.130 --> 25:08.131
dissenters arrested, killed.

25:08.132 --> 25:10.342
Social media, we have co-opted them.

25:10.343 --> 25:12.802
Information technology, we have used them.

25:12.803 --> 25:14.387
They all follow the same play book.

25:14.388 --> 25:18.516
Now it fits, now it fits how you
make journalists and critics

25:18.517 --> 25:20.895
and activists enemies of the state.

25:21.520 --> 25:24.356
If you don’t have facts,
you can’t have truth.

25:24.357 --> 25:26.233
Without truth, you can’t
have trust.

25:26.234 --> 25:29.027
If you don’t have any of these three,

25:29.028 --> 25:30.737
you don’t have a shared reality.

25:30.738 --> 25:32.822
You can't solve any...

25:32.823 --> 25:34.783
like let alone existential problems

25:34.784 --> 25:37.244
like climate change,
you can’t solve any problem.

25:37.245 --> 25:39.247
You cannot have democracy.

25:41.916 --> 25:45.419
Isn’t this a science fiction
movie?

26:01.018 --> 26:03.729
