were commodified,

48:56.392 --> 48:58.727
it was the age of industrialisation,

48:58.728 --> 49:00.228
and it was labour,

49:00.229 --> 49:02.731
and when labour was commodified,

49:02.732 --> 49:05.776
we had sweatshops, we had factory lines,

49:05.777 --> 49:07.194
we had child labour,

49:07.195 --> 49:13.033
we had exploitation
of our physical bodies.

49:13.034 --> 49:16.578
Now what’s commodified is not
our physical bodies,

49:16.579 --> 49:19.082
it’s our attention.

49:24.128 --> 49:26.381
So what are they going to do next?

49:35.139 --> 49:39.852
In 2017, a new AI engine got invented.

49:41.270 --> 49:44.147
These things are generative,
large language,

49:44.148 --> 49:46.401
multimodal models.

49:48.403 --> 49:52.990
These models treat absolutely
everything as language.

49:58.413 --> 50:02.750
